data.description: Modern move-in ready home in Silverado Ranch, minutes away from the I-15 & 215 freeways.  Cozy 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 baths. Upgraded Kitchen has white cabinets & quartz countertops. Stainless Steel Appliances, Wood-like plank tiles throughout entire house!!!!Low maintenance desert landscaping. A large patio to enjoy the beautiful weather.  Recently, updated community parks & immaculately maintained pools. Recently, added overflow parking for your convenience. Must See!! Can be YOURS TODAY!
